Package: JAOPuTo
Type: Package
Title: Access JAO Publication Tool API
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Nico Schoutteet
Maintainer: Nico Schoutteet <n.schoutteet@gmail.com>
Description: Provides functions to retrieve and process data from the JAO Publication Tool API.
    The package includes automatic splitting of long time intervals, rate limiting
    and consistent parsing of API responses into tidy data structures.
